What Is B2B Programmatic Advertising in 2025?
B2B programmatic advertising is the automated buying and selling of digital ads using technology platforms that rely on data signals, AI algorithms, and real-time bidding. Unlike traditional advertising, where ad placements are manual and time-consuming, programmatic uses real-time data to serve ads to specific decision-makers at the moment they are most likely to engage.

In 2025, programmatic has evolved to serve more than display ads. It now powers:

Connected TV (CTV) advertising

Audio ads

Native ads

Video placements

Social retargeting

Digital out-of-home (DOOH)

Account-based advertising

This gives B2B companies unprecedented reach across channels where business buyers spend their time.

